snippet: Boeing said it also set company records for orders in 2014, booking 1,550 gross orders.
abstract: Boeing reports delivery of 723 jetliners in 2014, setting industry record and retaining title as world's biggest plane maker.
lead_paragraph: Boeing said it also set company records for orders in 2014, booking 1,550 gross orders.

headline.main: With 2014 Deliveries, Boeing Keeps Title as Top Plane Maker
